Draft Tees Valley Combined Authority (Adult Education Functions) Order 2018                  The Committee consisted of the following Members:            Chair: David Hanson            † Allan, Lucy (Telford) (Con)            † Bacon, Mr Richard (South Norfolk) (Con)            † Brereton, Jack (Stoke-on-Trent South) (Con)            † Clarke, Mr Simon (Middlesbrough South and East Cleveland) (Con)            † Cunningham, Alex (Stockton North) (Lab)            Daby, Janet (Lewisham East) (Lab)            † Ellman, Dame Louise (Liverpool, Riverside) (Lab/Co-op)            Fitzpatrick, Jim (Poplar and Limehouse) (Lab)            † Fletcher, Colleen (Coventry North East) (Lab)            † Johnson, Dr Caroline (Sleaford and North Hykeham) (Con)            † Kyle, Peter (Hove) (Lab)            † Marsden, Gordon (Blackpool South) (Lab)            † Mercer, Johnny (Plymouth, Moor View) (Con)            † Milling, Amanda (Cannock Chase) (Con)            † Milton, Anne (Minister for Apprenticeships and Skills)            † Streeting, Wes (Ilford North) (Lab)            † Swire, Sir Hugo (East Devon) (Con)            Dominic Stockbridge, Committee Clerk            † attended the Committee            Fifth Delegated Legislation Committee            Tuesday 16 October 2018            [David Hanson in the Chair ]            Draft Liverpool City Region Combined Authority (Adult Education Functions) Order 2018           8.55 am        The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:     This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.     The Minister for Apprenticeships and Skills (Anne Milton)       Share       I beg to move, That the Committee has considered the draft Liverpool City Region Combined Authority (Adult Education Functions) Order 2018.     Share          The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:     This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.     The Chair       Share       With 